<i>(Lekcia Párenia)</i>

277
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,270
PRILOŽÍME RUKU K DIELU?

278
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:20,520
PRILOŽÍME RUKU NA DIERU?

279
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,860
To je ale obrovská kuchyňa.

280
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:25,800
Dejima-san, si dobrá v príprave sladkostí?

281
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:26,780
Áno.

282
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,750
Dokážem urobiť čokoľvek.

283
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:30,690
Japonské jedlá,

284
00:11:30,690 --> 00:11:32,550
Západné jedlá, sladkosti...

285
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:33,780
Muža...

286
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:36,400
Tak, začnime s prípravou.

287
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:36,920
Dobre.

288
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:39,290
Čože? Nepočuli ma?

289
00:11:41,290 --> 00:11:45,050
Viete, Dejima-san mi zachránila život.

290
00:11:45,050 --> 00:11:46,290
Ako sa to stalo?

291
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:47,790
Minulú noc...

292
00:11:50,190 --> 00:11:51,170
Pozor!

293
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,580
Takmer som spadla a zranila sa

294
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:56,720
Počkaj chvíľu.

295
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,810
Čo tam vlastne Dejima-san robila?

296
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,940
Teraz si pripravíme vzory.

297
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,440
Vyhodilo istič.

298
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:07,170
Mladá pani, kde ste?!

299
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:08,460
Ozvite sa mi.

300
00:12:08,460 --> 00:12:10,170
Som v poriadku.

301
00:12:10,930 --> 00:12:16,410
Je tma a mohlo by sa diať niečo erotické, no ja to nevidím!

302
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,950
Cítim zlú energiu.

303
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:21,110
Sakra.

304
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:23,090
Čo je?

305
00:12:23,090 --> 00:12:23,710
Čo sa stalo?

306
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:27,210
Chcela som zistiť, či čokoláda už stuhla,

307
00:12:27,210 --> 00:12:30,090
no pošmykla som sa a moja ruka...

308
00:12:30,090 --> 00:12:33,450
Nie, to nemusí byť tak zlé.

309
00:12:33,450 --> 00:12:35,970
Hej, prináša to späť spomienky.

310
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:38,890
Vieš, keď si bola malá a chcela vidieť, ako rastieš.

311
00:12:38,890 --> 00:12:41,220
V poriadku. Idem to hneď prerobiť.

312
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,950
Takatoshi-kun.

313
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:46,130
Tu máš odo mňa čokoládu.

314
00:12:46,130 --> 00:12:47,520
Odo mňa tiež.

315
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,610
Ďakujem.

316
00:12:49,090 --> 00:12:51,060
Hej, Tsuda, neprepadni im!

317
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:52,240
Presne!

318
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:54,840
Ak si chceš vybrať, buď najprv vyberavý (tsundere)!

319
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,490
